<text>This is a list of the districts of England ordered by population, according to estimated figures for from the Office for National Statistics.

The list consists of 164 non-metropolitan districts, 32 London boroughs, 36 metropolitan boroughs, 62 unitary authorities, and two &quot;sui generis&quot; authorities (the City of London and the Isles of Scilly).


